<p>In the code below I ping array of destination addresses and expect number of pings to be counted. I am suing callback(counterReplied,counterPinged) function for this. But my response is 0/0 , see below</p>  <pre><code>var counterPinged = 0; var counterReplied = 0; var counterDead = 0; function pingall(callback) {     targets.forEach(function (host) {         ping.sys.probe(host, function (isAlive) {                         counterPinged++;             if (isAlive) {                 counterReplied++;                 console.log('Replied: ', counterReplied + '/' + counterPinged, host);             } else counterDead++;         });     });     callback(counterReplied,counterPinged); }  pingall(function(Replied, Pinged) {     console.log(Replied + '/' + Pinged) }); </code></pre>  <p>and the sample result (ping itself look fine, except total of 6 were pinged..):</p>  <pre><code>0/0     Replied:  1/1 10.199.107.1     Replied:  2/2 10.199.108.1     Replied:  3/3 10.199.109.1     Replied:  4/4 10.200.107.1 </code></pre>